trans-unit.source: Enumerates the elements of a <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Queue`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 列舉 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Queue`1" /> 的項目。

trans-unit.source: The `foreach` statement of the C# language (`for each` in C++, `For Each` in Visual Basic) hides the complexity of the enumerators.
trans-unit.target: `foreach` C# 語言的陳述式 (`for each` c + +`For Each`在 Visual Basic 中) 會隱藏列舉值的複雜度。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, using `foreach` is recommended, instead of directly manipulating the enumerator.
trans-unit.target: 因此，建議您使用 `foreach`，而不要直接使用列舉值。

trans-unit.source: Enumerators can be used to read the data in the collection, but they cannot be used to modify the underlying collection.
trans-unit.target: 列舉程式可以用來讀取集合中的資料，但是無法用來修改基礎集合。

trans-unit.source: Initially, the enumerator is positioned before the first element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 一開始，列舉程式位在集合中的第一個項目之前。

trans-unit.source: At this position, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 在這個位置上，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> 並未定義。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, you must call <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> to advance the enumerator to the first element of the collection before reading the value of <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 因此，在讀取 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> 的值之前，必須呼叫 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> 以將列舉值前移至集合的第一個項目。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> returns the same object until <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> 會傳回相同的物件直到呼叫 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> sets <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> to the next element.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> 會將 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> 設定為下一個項目。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> passes the end of the collection, the enumerator is positioned after the last element in the collection and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> returns `false`.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>超過集合的列舉值的結尾會位於集合中的最後一個元素之後和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>傳回`false`。

trans-unit.source: When the enumerator is at this position, subsequent calls to <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> also return `false`.
trans-unit.target: 列舉值位於這個位置上，後續呼叫<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>也會傳回`false`。

trans-unit.source: If the last call to <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> returned `false`, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 如果最後一個呼叫<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>傳回`false`，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A>是未定義。

trans-unit.source: You cannot set <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> to the first element of the collection again; you must create a new enumerator instance instead.
trans-unit.target: 您不能再次將 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> 設定為集合的第一個項目；您必須建立新的列舉值執行個體。

trans-unit.source: An enumerator remains valid as long as the collection remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: 只要集合維持不變，列舉程式就持續有效。

trans-unit.source: If changes are made to the collection, such as adding, modifying, or deleting elements, the enumerator is irrecoverably invalidated and the next call to <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> or <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.System%23Collections%23IEnumerator%23Reset%2A> throws an <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>.
trans-unit.target: 如果變更集合，例如加入、 修改或刪除項目，列舉程式會永久失效，而且下次呼叫<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>或<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.System%23Collections%23IEnumerator%23Reset%2A>會擲回<xref:System.InvalidOperationException>。

trans-unit.source: If the collection is modified between calling <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> method and obtaining the value of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> property, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> returns the element that it is set to, even if the enumerator is already invalidated.
trans-unit.target: 如果呼叫之間修改集合<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>方法並取得的值<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A>屬性，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A>傳回項目所設定，即使列舉值已經無效。

trans-unit.source: The enumerator does not have exclusive access to the collection; therefore, enumerating through a collection is intrinsically not a thread-safe procedure.
trans-unit.target: 列舉程式沒有集合的獨佔存取權，因此，列舉集合內容本質上並不是安全的執行緒程序。

trans-unit.source: To guarantee thread safety during enumeration, you can lock the collection during the entire enumeration.
trans-unit.target: 若要確保列舉期間的執行緒安全性，您可以在整個列舉期間鎖定集合。

trans-unit.source: To allow the collection to be accessed by multiple threads for reading and writing, you must implement your own synchronization.
trans-unit.target: 若要讓多重執行緒能夠存取集合以便進行讀取和寫入，您必須實作自己的同步處理。

trans-unit.source: Default implementations of collections in <xref:System.Collections.Generic?displayProperty=nameWithType> are not synchronized.
trans-unit.target: 集合中的預設實作<xref:System.Collections.Generic?displayProperty=nameWithType>未同步處理。

trans-unit.source: Gets the element at the current position of the enumerator.
trans-unit.target: 取得位於目前列舉值位置的項目。

trans-unit.source: The element in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Queue`1" /> at the current position of the enumerator.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Queue`1" /> 中位於目前列舉值位置的項目。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> throws an <xref:System.InvalidOperationException> under any of the following conditions:
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> 擲回<xref:System.InvalidOperationException>任何下列情況：

trans-unit.source: The enumerator is positioned before the first element of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 列舉程式位在集合中第一個項目之前。

trans-unit.source: That happens after an enumerator is created or after the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.System%23Collections%23IEnumerator%23Reset%2A> method is called.
trans-unit.target: 發生這種情況建立列舉值之後或在之後<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.System%23Collections%23IEnumerator%23Reset%2A>方法呼叫。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> method must be called to advance the enumerator to the first element of the collection before reading the value of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>必須呼叫方法，將列舉值前進到第一個項目，再讀取的值集合的<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A>屬性。

trans-unit.source: The last call to <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> returned `false`, which indicates the end of the collection and that the enumerator is positioned after the last element of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 在上次呼叫<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>傳回`false`，表示集合的結尾，列舉程式位在集合中的最後一個元素之後。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> does not move the position of the enumerator, and consecutive calls to <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> return the same object until either <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> or <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.System%23Collections%23IEnumerator%23Reset%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> 不會移動的列舉程式及連續呼叫位置<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A>傳回相同的物件直到<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>或<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.System%23Collections%23IEnumerator%23Reset%2A>呼叫。

trans-unit.source: If the collection is modified between calling <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> method and obtaining the value of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> property, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> returns the element that it is set to, even though the enumerator is invalidated.
trans-unit.target: 如果呼叫之間修改集合<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>方法並取得的值<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A>屬性，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A>傳回的項目設定為時，即使列舉值無效。

trans-unit.source: The enumerator is positioned before the first element of the collection or after the last element.
trans-unit.target: 列舉值是放在集合的第一個項目之前，或最後一個項目之後。

trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Queue`1.Enumerator" />.
trans-unit.target: 釋放 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Queue`1.Enumerator" /> 所使用的所有資源。

trans-unit.source: Advances the enumerator to the next element of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Queue`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 將列舉值前移至 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Queue`1" /> 的下一個項目。

trans-unit.source: After an enumerator is created, the enumerator is positioned before the first element in the collection, and the first call to <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> advances the enumerator to the first element of the collection.
